Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:12.29,Vinland-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1626,891)}{\fad(800,1000)\blur7}#14  曉光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.68,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：《聖經舊約·耶利米哀歌》第5章第21句。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,耶和華啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:16.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,求你使我們迴轉歸向你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就得以迴轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,求你更新我們的年日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:27.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,像古時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  神父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了  我和這位大哥就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:45.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從小做什麼事都是一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.76,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來都互相幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,戰場上的默契不輸任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,說的沒錯  我們心靈相通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我能託付後背的人只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:06.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種信賴用銀幣也換不來的吧  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話  老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也得看有多少金額
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的兄弟情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你說的愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:21.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底對不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:29.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是和我想像中的愛完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊  神父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有上過戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂這種默契的厲害之處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,生死之間的配合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這是很美好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:52.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對於你們兄弟來說應該是無價之寶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  假如我站上了戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你會保護我的後背嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了只有跟大哥才做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會把後背交給一個酒鬼僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  你能不能說得簡單一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:28.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你那麼喜歡酒  這個酒不就是愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:34.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  而且我並不喜歡酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就別喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這人莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是好在莫名其妙這一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你聽聽看這個故事怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:49.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在老團員之間這事至今還是會被提起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:53.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們曾經在法羅群島襲擊船舶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.79,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船上有一個戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的是太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們全部人都攻了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:08.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那人空著手一下子就把三十個人打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,空著手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然最後他被我們幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是事後我們清點損失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,發現居然沒有死人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,當時到底是什麼情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙好像背著一把劍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該是被小看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣的話就太讓人火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一點作為戰士的禮貌都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人還做了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,名字不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:52.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的人之間果然是臭味相投的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傢伙也說了些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:07:00.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,「真正的戰士不需要劍」來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  怎麼了  僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等…你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,僧侶  你到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的說對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:38.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,戰士…真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的…戰士…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:06.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我說也沒用  要怪就怪這天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個船員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,海上還好說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,陸地的天氣我可不好預測
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,更不可能預料到剛入冬就積了那麼厚的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:26.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說你的時運沒那麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到雪天就急著改變行進路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果一下成這樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的很多士兵都已經開始動搖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:38.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手下都有過無數次出生入死的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度的天氣才不會怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不都在俐落地聽從命令行進著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,返回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,橫跨麥西亞是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:57.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,撥開雪前進的話就得丟掉戰利品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,手下們怕是不願意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚已經沒辦法露營了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿謝拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:12.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿謝拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:21.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有時運的時候  做什麼都不會如意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,朗納爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要這麼猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,襲擊  掠奪村落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我們諾爾斯人的傳統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.09,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：語出《聖經新約·馬太福音》第6章第11-13句，講述耶穌教導信眾如何禱告的情節。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在天上的父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們日用的飲食  今日賜給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:57.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,免我們的債  如同我們免了人的債
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:02.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不叫我們陷入試探  救我們脫離那惡者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:05.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為國度  權柄  榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,全是你的  直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:10.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼總是要祈禱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為耶穌要讓我們這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,耶穌說的話不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不祈禱會發生什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信他的人死後就會落入地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:42.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,地獄很可怕  裡頭全是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,惡魔很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:54.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是會祈禱的好孩子能去天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是沒什麼實感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:06.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不久以後大家就要被帶到天堂或者地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想一家人都被迫分開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:16.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼神突然決定要審判這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不突然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他很早以前就決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:24.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就定在耶穌復活一千年後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是二十年後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:24.39,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：末日審判的其中一種預言假說，當時一些基督徒宣稱，\N世界末日將在耶穌死後復活一千年（1033年）降臨。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神會降下審判
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,壞人全都將下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:39.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,壞人就是丹麥人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  他們超級壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:50.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神一定知道會有那樣的人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:55.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要好好聽耶穌的教誨…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:56.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:00.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去小便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,又戴上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個戒指要花多少錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:49.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在付錢的話  神還會原諒我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是來自惡魔的誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明連錢都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:08.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就不該去逛集市的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣的壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會在審判之日下地獄的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡肯定只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,無法去天國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,戴在左手也真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那張臉算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會  我也會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的話沒聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好做個好孩子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神會懲罰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:25.93,Vinland-picture - v2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\frz270\pos(1248,246)}你竟全然拋棄我們，\N向我們大發雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:25.93,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,《聖經舊約·耶利米哀歌》第5章第22節。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個村子已經被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,丹麥人  要將這個村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:39.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚷嚷你這臭僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真暖和  活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這一家是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好多小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:57.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大麥  牛奶粥和一點肉乾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,放了洋蔥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把能當武器的東西都收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:07.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:17.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.76,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你們吃得下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:28.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,浪費糧食會遭天譴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.32,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:35.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那什麼  用英格蘭語怎麼說的來著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,交出所有吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.70,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:55.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,交出所有吃的  不然殺光你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:01.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,2個小孩算1個人  就一共有50人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說越冬的儲糧也差不多是50人的量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對104名戰士來說有點不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:32.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是王子的教師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是這個兵團的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只原諒你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果下次還礙事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,當場就把你殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來就討厭僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是丹麥人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:07.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有通曉我們語言的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:16.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.64,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,能把一半食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能給我們留下一半嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有一半食物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天就能想辦法熬過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,村裡還有嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:31.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還請大發慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嬰兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的事情已經考慮過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不用擔心越冬的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論明年還是後年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,都不用擔心越冬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們從苦惱中解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿謝拉特  他們都是非戰鬥人員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:15.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們活著也沒有給他們吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是逃走了一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:21.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就有可能暴露我們還在敵人腹地磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是萬萬受不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  坑挖好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:27.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,擠一擠可以容得下六十人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:34.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿謝拉特  這些人是基督教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是保護王子最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:44.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼其他人有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:47.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼弟兄們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:00.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽  爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有弟弟和妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到您身邊去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:29.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您果然不喜歡我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢  因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怦然心動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:52.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有  居然有如此壞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:58.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有這麼多人不懼怕您的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:05.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同偷走戒指時的那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怦然心動了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,——ED——
